features.additionalInfo: Shop online or in store with our rediCard or Visa Debit card
First 5 ATM withdrawals and first 5 EFTPOS debits each month as well as all online banking and smartPAY App transactions are fee free
By increasing your total balance (deposits and loans) through saving, investing and borrowing with us, you pay fewer transaction costs.
The easy way to pay everyday with Apple Pay
The convenience of a mobile wallet in your hands with Google Pay
24/7 access to your accounts anywhere in the world with our smartPAY App. You can also temporarily block your card or report it lost or stolen.
Secure banking 24/7 from your computer or mobile with Online Banking
Receive fast real-time payments using your mobile number, email address or ABN instead of your BSB and account number
Send and receive real-time payments via Osko from your Online Banking and NICU smartPay App
Receive notifications for transactions and balances on your accounts via sms

features.additionalValue: Automatic data feeds to your chosen accounting software
features.additionalInfo: Give your accountant access to your financial statements via online accounting software such as Banklink and Xero
Access your personal account wherever you see an Australia Post retail outlet displaying the Bank@Post™ sign, if you have a card linked to the account on which you want to transact.
